description: Client-side JavaScript for handling contact form submission. No AJAX calls to backend - form submission is simulated client-side only.
notes: Contains contact form handler that prevents default submission and shows success message. No actual form backend. No AJAX, fetch, or API calls. jQuery, Popper, and Bootstrap JS loaded from CDN: https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js, https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js, https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js
